{"_id":"AXJVjPupM4UQ0z2t","name":"Zero-G Nausea","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>This trait is only available to biomorphs. This morph suffers from space sickness and does not fare well in zero gravity. Apply a -10 impairment modifier in any microgravity climate. Additionally, the first time you must acclimate or endure excessive movement in microgravity, you must make a SOM Check or spend 1 hour incapacitated by nausea.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 80","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"allActions"}],"modifier":-10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"in microgravity","id":"je47t8kso0"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"First time must acclimate or endure excessive movement in micrograv, make a SOM Check or be incapacitated by nausea for 1 hour","id":"tms2w2okpj"}],"id":"253k97i3ac"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Bls1VQ84lpQaDPzT","name":"Quickness","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Either your morph is dexterous or you take full advantage of its nimbleness. Apply +5 per level to REF Checks.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 75","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"ref"}],"modifier":5,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"zogajr483h"}],"id":"pxnjko00ud"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"ref"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"zogajr483h"}],"id":"rs9j693mof"},{"cost":3,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"ref"}],"modifier":15,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"zogajr483h"}],"id":"md6y0eyhat"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Cg5MylRwzuaXldRP","name":"Danger Sense","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>You possess an intuitive sixth sense that warns of imminent threats. It provides a +10 modifier to Perceive Tests to avoid surprise ▶227.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 73","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skill","skillType":"perceive"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"vs surprise","id":"xca6ufnyiz"}],"id":"36of9drn5y"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
