{"_id":"JixeRVxoj8FesLHZ","name":"Natural Immunity","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>This trait is only available to biomorphs. The morph has a natural immunity to a specific drug, disease, or toxin. When afflicted with that specific chemical, poison, or pathogen, you are unaffected. Work with your GM to select an appropriate agent; this immunity may not be applied to nanodrugs or nanotoxins.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 74","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You are immune to this drug, disease or toxin (choose one)","id":"qkrm5ednyy"}],"id":"q2sd0ilc89"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"K7UuE2rwLQV0NAl3","name":"Skill Artifact","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>The morph has latent skills stored in its muscle memory or as higher-level data that somehow does not get erased or overwritten. The GM chooses or randomly selects a skill; it is recommended to pick a skill linked to the morph’s highest pool. You receive a +10 modifier per level when using that skill. This trait may be purchased multiple times for different skills.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 75","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skill","skillType":"athletics"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"hukt0dbw9t"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Needs player correction","id":"qphuh9c5f6"}],"id":"pir848wec2"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skill","skillType":"athletics"}],"modifier":20,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"hukt0dbw9t"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Needs player correction","id":"viaqut5chk"}],"id":"uwzh4r4iuq"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"KL7kO7lqEMFUFZX6","name":"Indifference","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Your social awareness is often lacking. You suffer -5 per level to SAV Checks.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"sav"}],"modifier":-5,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"fmh3129dhc"}],"id":"kyx3qt0enp"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"sav"}],"modifier":-10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"fmh3129dhc"}],"id":"23y1ndd9u1"},{"cost":3,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"sav"}],"modifier":-15,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"fmh3129dhc"}],"id":"q02qs540ne"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"KPlAIEw9KKb7CKMi","name":"Hyper Linguistics","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>You have a natural gift with linguistic structures and syntax. You receive a +10 modifier to INT Checks per level to grasp the general meaning or intent of communication spoken in languages you don’t know — even alien tongues. This trait provides no bonuses to written texts or non-verbal communications (such as Factor spores).</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 74","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"communicating in spoken languages you don't know","id":"xrrzovyven"}],"id":"bxzfzm7bzh"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":20,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"communicating in spoken languages you don't know","id":"xrrzovyven"}],"id":"fbty4en343"},{"cost":3,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":30,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"communicating in spoken languages you don't know","id":"xrrzovyven"}],"id":"7azejjpdsg"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"L5xO64kkXhTrM3Fq","name":"Skill Glitch","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Some unfixable glitch in the morph’s hardware or brain structure impedes the use of one particular skill, chosen or randomly selected by the GM. Apply a -10 modifier per level to that skill’s use.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 80","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skill","skillType":"athletics"}],"modifier":-10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"z987zw9fcg"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Needs player correction","id":"rlzt08wm32"}],"id":"awjsfnldt9"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skill","skillType":"athletics"}],"modifier":-20,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"z987zw9fcg"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Needs player correction","id":"4wmz11irl1"}],"id":"9tmpeh722f"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Lt6tPhcbsfYSPQS4","name":"Blacklisted Rep","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>You are blacklisted in certain circles, whether you did something to deserve it or not. You are barred from having a Rep score higher than 0 in one particular reputation network. For rep nets outside your faction, this counts as Level 1. For the rep net central to your faction, this counts as Level 2. People within that network will refuse to help you out of fear of reprisals and ruining their own reputation. This trait may be taken more than once for different rep nets.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 77","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Cannot have rep score in one rep network","id":"4rcdi01v0m"}],"id":"2mmy7c7668"},{"cost":4,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Cannot have rep score in your own faction's network","id":"2m0a24my81"}],"id":"njau10qw1f"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"MsDMceAsFBsgmb31","name":"Expert Training","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>You have received extensive training in one particular subject. You may raise one skill over 80, to a maximum of 90, during character creation. This trait does not actually increase the skill, it just raises the maximum.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 74","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You may raise one skill over to a maximum of 90 during character creation","id":"fwspblet98"}],"id":"v64w445u94"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"NbZsOfj7Sc7uS0uw","name":"Sensitive","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Your brain’s operating system is vulnerable to exploits. Apply a -10 modifier per level to INT Checks made to resist basilisk hacks.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 80","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":-10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"resisting basilisk hacks","id":"hzqmra9h1q"}],"id":"mwlckq5cym"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":-20,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"resisting basilisk hacks","id":"hzqmra9h1q"}],"id":"1qg2p0o8mx"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Nh3Bk18Py19qIkeQ","name":"Planned Obsolecense","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>The morph is designed in such a way that it needs periodic genetic service pack therapy or proprietary maintenance or its performance will degrade. Treat this as a Moderate Complexity service required every month. For each month this is skipped, reduce the morph’s pools by 1 (the GM chooses which pool). If pools are reduced to 0, the morph incurs 1 wound per month that may not be repaired or healed. These manifest as joint pain, neural degradation, tumors, and other malfunctions. Once 4 wounds are accumulated, the morph is incapacitated. A gene therapy or maintenance session from a licensed hypercorp service provider (or a black market pirate) will restore the morph to full functionality.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 79","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You need monthly maintenace on your morph or your it will start losing it's pools","id":"4m131t2n1k"}],"id":"maqxfyzwjq"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"OaMwnqYiK6NE6f0I","name":"Good Instinct","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Your gut feelings are on target. You get +5 per level to INT Checks.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 74","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":5,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"c1wkpzyt7n"}],"id":"wnn2b2zfjq"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"c1wkpzyt7n"}],"id":"89qqy0c03o"},{"cost":3,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":15,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"c1wkpzyt7n"}],"id":"vm7utb7rfc"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
