{"_id":"PlOGsmfVxRGeTSmZ","name":"Enhanced Behavior","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Your conduct or moods are modified. This may be due to conditioning and reprogramming via time-accelerated psychosurgery ▶294, drugs, genetic tweaks, psi, or other factors. This may have been a deliberate choice or it may have been inflicted against your will. Work with your GM to define a specific emotion (e.g., happiness, contentment, love) or behavior (e.g., aggression, commitment, curiosity, orderliness, loyalty). Apply a -10 modifier per level to all actions when withheld from the behavior/emotion.</p><p>Level 1: You are encouraged to pursue the behavior and associate it with positive feelings; emotions are boosted.</p><p>Level 2: You are driven to engage in the specified behavior; emotions are exaggerated. Holding back requires a WIL Check.</p><p>Level 3: The behavior is enforced; emotions are compulsory and ongoing. If restrained from the conduct or the emotion is suppressed, suffer SV 1d6.</p><p>This trait may be taken more than once for different behaviors.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 78","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"allActions"}],"modifier":-10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"withheld from behavior/emotion","id":"unpmong88t"}],"id":"fngiund4yp"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"allActions"}],"modifier":-20,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"withheld from behavior/emotion","id":"cgx0t1h7ch"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Holding back requires a WIL Check","id":"qcskn12n5u"}],"id":"tgi795dt5c"},{"cost":4,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"allActions"}],"modifier":-30,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"withheld from behavior/emotion","id":"nsjss6h3ns"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"If restrained from conduct or suppressing the emotion, suffer SV 1d6","id":"yp1twi8nwr"}],"id":"prw6g3i4gq"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
