{"_id":"V1UME476Vxpf804w","name":"Combat Paralysis","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Like a deer caught in headlights, you freeze in combat and stressful situations. Anytime violence erupts, you are caught off guard, or lives are at stake, you must make a WIL Check each action turn to act or respond in any way. If you fail, you lose your action and simply stand there, incapable of reacting to the situation.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 77","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":4,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You must make a WIL check per action turn in stressful situations or lose your action","id":"vv0kzr79yw"}],"id":"6o1shit2a7"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Vw8lpQ294NbGCut4","name":"No Backup Insurance","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>You are either poor, bioconservative, or like to live dangerously. You do not have any sort of backup insurance or similar arrangement. If you die, your stack's retrieval and your ego's re-instantiation is entirely dependent upon the circumstances and GM. You may be brought back with significantly lower MP or be permanently dead.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 79","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You're lacking any backup insurance or similar arrangement","id":"clkv95deuq"}],"id":"xin6j2esxf"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"WDzYNEwpDv4iYKYK","name":"Proprietary Tech","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>This trait is only available to synthmorphs. This morph was built with non-standard specifications, making most modern tools and software incompatible. This is a conscious design decision to make the user dependent upon the manufacturer for repairs and updates. Fixer nanoswarms will not work on this morph and Hardware: Robotics Tests suffer a -20 modifier.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 80","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"morph","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"fieldSkill","fieldSkill":"hardware","field":"Robotics"}],"modifier":-20,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"working on this morph","id":"893l49x1gz"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Fixer and nanoswarms will not work on this morph","id":"6qhgz8xyo1"}],"id":"c5y7ffnmzd"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"WLbLPwQQTDwCss0q","name":"Restricted Behavior","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>Your conduct or moods are modified. This may be due to conditioning and reprogramming via time-accelerated psychosurgery ▶294, drugs, genetic tweaks, psi, or other factors. This may have been a deliberate choice or it may have been inflicted against your will. Work with your GM to define a specific emotion (e.g., sadness, anxiety, anger, inhibitions) or behavior (e.g., aggression, stealing, eating, lying, using a specific drug). Apply a -10 modifier per level to all actions when the behavior/emotion is not avoided.</p><p>Level 1: You are compelled to avoid the behavior and associate it with negative feelings; emotions are limited.</p><p>Level 2: You are blocked from the specified behavior; emotions are suppressed. Pursuing it requires a WIL Check.</p><p>Level 3: You are incapable of pursuing the behavior; emotions are expunged. If forced to engage in the conduct or to experience the emotion, suffer SV 1d6.</p><p>This trait may be taken more than once for different behaviors.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 80","restrictions":"","triggers":"","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":1,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"allActions"}],"modifier":-10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"engaging in behavior/emotion","id":"44rnufou8x"}],"id":"mscqiwd1zn"},{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"allActions"}],"modifier":-20,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"engaging in behavior/emotion","id":"44rnufou8x"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Engaging in it requires a WIL Check","id":"krm8xo8dun"}],"id":"vjxfyptxyb"},{"cost":4,"effects":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"allActions"}],"modifier":-30,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"engaging in behavior/emotion","id":"44rnufou8x"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"If forced to engage in conduct or experiencing emotion, suffer SV 1d6","id":"ev3wftw3js"}],"id":"26wk8y25wh"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"negative"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
